WEBVTT

00:10:59.400 --> 00:11:01.736
we need a new radical humanism.

00:11:01.760 --> 00:11:06.160
We must acquire and promote
a new aesthetic and sentimental education.

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:08.680
Because if we don't,

00:11:09.360 --> 00:11:11.816
we might end up feeling like aliens

00:11:11.840 --> 00:11:15.856
in organizations and societies
that are full of smart machines

00:11:15.880 --> 00:11:18.696
that have no appreciation whatsoever

00:11:18.720 --> 00:11:20.336
for the unnecessary,

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:21.616
the intimate,

00:11:21.640 --> 00:11:23.336
the incomplete

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:25.040
and definitely not for the ugly.

00:11:25.760 --> 00:11:26.976
Thank you.

00:11:27.000 --> 00:11:31.862
(Applause)